data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. WELCOME HOME to Your Very Own Private Peace of Paradise located in the community of Lakeside Plantation! This stunning, spacious, immaculate Split Bedroom Open Floor Plan POOL/SPA HOME has been IMPECCABLY MAINTAINED. A One-Level, Single-Family Home with 2 car garage at the end of a quiet cul de sac. New Roof (12/2022), New Luxury Vinyl Plank waterproof flooring in main living area (2023), New Water Heater (2022), Pool Cage- full refurbishment (2023), New ceiling fans, whole house water softener and the list goes on an on... Only a short walk to the many community amenities. Location, Location, Location!  Lakeside Plantation is located within the Highly Rated Sarasota County School District, in the Dynamite Community of North Port, Florida, rated as one of the Top 10 Fastest Growing Cities in the U.S.  Centrally located, Minutes to I-75, US-41. Within 2 miles of shopping, restaurants, car services, doctors, SMH Emergency Medical and 4 miles to the upcoming new SMH Hospital. And soon we will have our own “Wellen Park” development just a mile across I-75- the amazing new “Toledo Village”. Low HOA fees include lawn and landscape maintenance so you can spend your weekend enjoying your pool. Not in a flood zone.  Furnishings are available under separate contract if that is your desire.
